title: Natalie Nunn on Reality TV, Being an Executive & Still Fighting on TV & More
description:
The one and only Natalie Nunn sat down with Gina, accompanied by Sharp, to tell us all the behind the scenes of Zeus' Baddies taking over the West Coast, as the executive producer.

----
00:00 Intro
1:18 Baddies South is currently the #1 show on Zeus
2:07 The evolution of Natalie Nunn, putting people on tv and the success of Baddies
6:00 Oxygen canceled the original BadGirls Club show, so Natalie revived the show
6:45 Baddies South, now doing Baddies West, the OG Bad Girls didn't want to f*ght so she recast for season 2
11:04 Sharp thinks the scenes are fake, Natalie explains how if girls have beef lets just film it
14:25 Some past Bad Girls Club are kinda hating and wanna f*ght Natalie in real life, most of them didn't believe in the vision and didn't believe in Zeus network
21:52 Natalie says the girl don't respect her, and will be fake to get on the show
26:46 Sharp wants to do the Baddies reunion
33:30 Natalie asks what defines a bad girl to him?
34:50 Sharp says a bad girl is someone who doesn't need validation, strong minded, challenging, about her business, it's a mindset
38:49 Natalie is looking for the next person she can put in position when she’s ready to hang it up and stay behind the scenes
45:14 Gina says Sharp is a rare breed, says most men are insecure
47:55 Natalie comes to realization that a woman who wants a real man should date a virgo man
48:50 Gina and Natalie only date insecure men, Sharp tells them that's not the way to go
50:00 The Blueface x Chr____ relationship, Natalie also producing their show on Zeus
1:01:31 Gina wants to get into the messiness, Natalie answers to the ___ _ allegations
1:06:21 Natalie on the fake girls tryna get on the show
1:08:14 People think Natalie and Curtis are an item
1:10:23 Every time Natalie is close to a man, ppl assume they're together, she's over it, Sharp doesn't believe her + Gina confirms that being a woman in the industry that's super common thing, Sharp doesn't believe it either
1:11:51 Natalie imitates Sharp's voice
1:15:20 Women are disrespected every time in this industry, Sharp doesn’t seem to know
1:17:06 Natalie OF leaked, some photos were clearly misinterpreted, ppl assumed they were together
1:18:43 Sharp asks if the have ever "bumped pocket books together"
1:20:39 Kirk Franklin's son coming out on Natalie's show
1:22:11 The Milan Christopher controversy, started a f*ght, then got his friend _ up instead, called the cops and hid in the bushes
1:23:45 Jonathan Wright was super lit, people loved him
1:26:37 Natalie and Maino getting into it in a NY club? Maino was lit and possibly didn't realize it was even Natalie and Zeus filming
1:30:18 Natalie posted chicken and waffles while flying private, had no idea about PNB's final moments
1:34:18 Natalie says Tanisha was trying to come in her show, but did not want to f*ght
1:40:41 Natalie speaks on Sara telling her she needs surgery when she's botched herself + Sara "conducting" a fake Natalie f*neral online was wild and disrespectful
1:42:28 Winter Blanco is always talking ish online about the show and about Nat, but Nat might bring her on the show
1:44:41 Sydney Starr did one season, then Nat wanted to try other girls, Sydney wasn't having it, she literally followed the girls every appearances they had and just re-inserted herself back to the show lol
1:51:35 Scottie got p*nched at the reunion?
1:55:57 Baddies coming to the West Coast finna be a crazy season

---
